        <item>
            <title>香港參與中國探月工程，嫦娥八號將攜同多功能機械人登月</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/17/hong-kong-lunar-robot/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=hong-kong-lunar-robot</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/17/hong-kong-lunar-robot/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[arthur]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 17 Mar 2025 01:00:19 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技新聞]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[INNOHK]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[創科]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[嫦娥八號]]>
            </category>
            <category>
